    <p>Placeholder. Explain how and when a customer can cancel, and any free-cancellation window.</p>
    <h2>2. Cancellation fees</h2>
    <p>Placeholder. Detail any fees for late cancellations or no-shows.</p>
    <h2>3. Rescheduling</h2>
    <p>Placeholder. Describe how to reschedule a visit.</p>
    <h2>4. Refunds</h2>
    <p>Placeholder. Explain refund eligibility, method, and processing timelines (including wallet credit).</p>
    <h2>5. Service quality concerns</h2>
    <p>Placeholder. Describe how to raise an issue and request a resolution.</p>
  </LegalPage>
</Layout>
